No. 618,

October Term, 1967.

Fortnightly Corp. v. United Artists Television, Inc., Irwin Karp on the motion.

392 U. S. 390. Motion of Authors League of America, Inc., for leave to file a brief, as amicus curiae, in support of rehearing granted. Petition for rehearing denied.

Mr. Justice Douglas, Mr. Justice Harlan, and Mr. Justice Marshall took no part in the consideration or decision of this motion and petition.
